|3 |    └─EXCHANGE IN DISTR                               |        |
|4 |      └─EXCHANGE OUT DISTR (HASH)                     |:EX10002|
|5 |        └─MATERIAL                                    |        |
|6 |          └─INDEX DELETE                              |t1(idx2)|
|7 |            └─EXCHANGE IN DISTR                       |        |
|8 |              └─EXCHANGE OUT DISTR (HASH)             |:EX10001|
|9 |                └─MATERIAL                            |        |
|10|                  └─UPDATE                            |        |
|11|                    └─EXCHANGE IN DISTR               |        |
|12|                      └─EXCHANGE OUT DISTR (PKEY HASH)|:EX10000|
|13|                        └─PX BLOCK ITERATOR           |        |
|14|                          └─TABLE FULL SCAN           |t1(idx2)|
====================================================================
